Make sure you display the party (or general 'Representatives') at the top.
Then, it should be a simple each loop with two <a> tags inside of it.
-->
<h1>{{represent}}</h1>
{{#each reps}}
<p><a href="/rep/{{this.representative.person.id}}">{{this.representative.person.name}}: </a><a href="/state/{{this.st}}">{{this.representative.state}}</a></p>
{{/each}}